FBIS4-10231 "drlat069_a_94020" FBIS-LAT-94-069 Daily Report 9 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba $10 Million Earmarked for Hospital Improvement $10 Million Earmarked for Hospital Improvement FL0904155294 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1000 GMT 9 Apr 94 FL0904155294 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [Text] The Public Health Ministry has earmarked $10 million for improving comfort and hygienic conditions at hospital centers. At the plenum of the national committee of the sector's workers union, it was reported that this money will cover the need for sheets and other materials, as well as products for cleaning and personal hygiene.
